0same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20by%20emptying%20the%20entire%20closet%2C%20creating%20categorized%20piles%20on%20my%20bed%20and%20floor.%20This%20section%20was%20for%20jeans%2C%20this%20other%20for%20shirts%2C%20this%20one%20for%20dresses%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20Of%20course%2C%20all%20the%20trash%20bags%20went%20to%20the%20hallway%20to%20be%20taken%20out%20at%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20closet%20was%20empty%2C%20it%20was%20time%20to%20decide%20what%20to%20keep%20and%20what%20to%20throw%20away.%20This%2C%20she%20told%20me%2C%20was%20the%20part%20people%20had%20the%20most%20difficult%20time%20with.%20And%20while%20I%20struggle%20with%20the%20physical%20act%20of%20throwing%20away%20stuff%20(because%20the%20trash%20is%20down%20three%20flights%20of%20stairs)%2C%20deciding%20when%20I'm%20over%20a%20piece%20of%20clothing%20has%20never%20been%20difficult.%20In%20fact%2C%20if%20I%20could%2C%20I'd%20reinvent%20my%20closet%20every%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20photos%20of%20cluttered%20closet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67190b5f01ea6d83dee36a87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20closet%20before%20(left)%20and%20after%20(right)%20being%20decluttered.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20all%20the%20piles%20around%20me%2C%20I%20felt%20incredibly%20overwhelmed%20and%20lost%20in%20the%20sea%20of%20stuff%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThis%20was%20the%20part%20where%20I'd%20probably%20give%20up%20if%20I%20were%20doing%20it%20by%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20put%20away%20the%20sections%2C%20as%20Millie%20gave%20me%20some%20organizing%20tips%20%E2%80%94%20while%20also%20letting%20me%20know%20there%20are%20no%20hard%20rules%20and%20I%20can%20change%20things%20up%20and%20make%20my%20own%20systems%20later%20if%20these%20didn't%20work%20for%20m