s-maharashtra-seat-sharing-with-state-congress-chief-nana-patole-sources-6818239%5C%22%3Eupcoming%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Maharashtra%20%3C%2Fa%3Etriggered%20the%20rift%20buzz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20veiled%20swipe%20of%20Sanjay%20Raut%20where%20he%20said%20the%20Congress%20leaders%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20capable%20of%20taking%20decisions%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Patole%20shot%20back%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20Sanjay%20Raut%20is%20controlling%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20that%20is%20their%20issue.%20We%20have%20the%20responsibility%20of%20telling%20the%20reality%20of%20our%20leaders%20and%20we%20are%20doing%20that.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20to%20speak%20anything%20on%20what%20Sanjay%20Raut%20does.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20however%2C%20played%20down%20the%20statements%20insisting%20that%20talks%20were%20going%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20event%2C%20Mr%20Patole%20also%20addressed%20the%20impasse%20between%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20in%20Maharashtra%20-%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20-%20over%20some%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20is%20a%20national%20party%2C%20and%20national%20parties%20have%20to%20handle%20things%20carefully.%20Regional%20parties%20have%20their%20demands%20and%20dreams%20of%20growth%2C%20which%20is%20acceptable.%20Congress%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20allocating%20seats%20based%20on%20merit%2C%20aiming%20for%20a%20majority%20government%20in%20Maharashtra.%20We%20are%20still%20working%20towards%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDiscussions%20for%205-10%20seats%20are%20still%20pending%2C%20and%20we'll%20resolve%20this%20issue.%20After%20October%2030%2C%20we'll%20gather%20again%20to%20find%20a%20solution.%20We%20have%20decided%20to%20contest%20elections%20as%20MVA.%20No%20conflicts%20arose%20during%20seat%20allocation.%20Efforts%20are%20continuing%20to%20resolve%20pending%20seat%20allocation%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C