%3BSpecial%20Train%20Did%20Not%20Arrive...%26quot%3B%3A%20Railway%20Commissioner%20On%20Bandra%20Stampede%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThane%20Central%20Railway%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20Manoj%20Nana%20Patil%20on%20Sunday%20attributed%20the%20stampede%20at%20Bandra%20Terminus%20to%20increased%20passenger%20rush%20due%20to%20the%20festive%20season%20and%20the%20unreserved%20nature%20of%20the%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Central%20Railway's%20announcement%20of%20two%20unreserved%20trains%20departing%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20Patil%20noted%20that%20the%20influx%20of%20passengers%20for%20the%20special%20train%20affected%20the%20Antyodaya%20Express%2C%20creating%20an%20overwhelming%20crowd%20that%20led%20to%20a%20stampede.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAntyodaya%20Express%20is%20a%20weekly%20train%20that%20runs%20every%20Sunday.%20Being%20unreserved%20and%20affordable%2C%20it%20usually%20attracts%20a%20high%20number%20of%20passengers.%20Due%20to%20the%20Diwali%20festival%2C%20the%20rush%20was%20unusually%20high.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20special%20train%20scheduled%20to%20run%20yesterday%20did%20not%20arrive%2C%20resulting%20in%20even%20more%20passengers%20converging%20here.%20Our%20team%20was%20present%2C%20but%20people%20suddenly%20rushed%20for%20seats.%20No%20one%20was%20critically%20injured%20in%20the%20incident...%20We%20are%20investigating%20the%20facts%2C%26quot%3B%20Manoj%20Nana%20Patil%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20eight%20individuals%20were%20reported%20injured%20in%20the%20stampede%20at%20Bandra%20Terminus%20today%2C%20according%20to%20an%20official%20statement%20by%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20around%2002%3A45%20hours%2C%20as%20passenger%20train%20number%2022921%20Antyodaya%20Express%20was%20slowly%20being%20brought%20onto%20platform%20number%201%20from%20the%20BDTS%20yard.%20Some%20passengers%20on%20the%20platform%20attempted%20to%20board%20the%20moving%20train%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20fall%20that%20resulted%20in%20injuries%20to%20two%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20RPF%2C%20GRP%2C%20and%20Home%20Guard%20officers%20on%20duty%20promptly%20admitted%20the%20injured%20to%20the%20Government%20Bhabha%20Hospital%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20injured%20passengers%20are%20now%20reported%20to%20be%20in%20stable%20condition%2C%20according%20to%20the%20medical%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20injured%2C%20five%20were%20admitted%20for%20treatment%2C%20while%20three%20opted%20to%20discharge%20themselves%20against%20medical%20advice%20(DAMA).%20Additionally%2C%20two%20patients%20were%20transferred%20to%20KEM%20Hospital%20for%20further%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20injured%20individuals%20are%20identified%20as%20Shabhir%20Abdul%20Rehman%20(40)%2C%20Sameer%20Shaikh%20(22)%2C%20Mohammad%20Shareef%20Shaikh%20(25)%2C%20Parmeshwar%20Sukhdar%20Gupta%20(28)%2C%20Ravindra%20Harihar%20Chuma%20(30)%2C%20Ramsevak%20Ravindra%20Prasad%20Prajapati%20(29)%2C%20Sanjay%20Tilakram%20Kangay%20(27)%2C%20and%20Divyanshu%20Yogendra%20Yadav%20(18).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20opposition%20leaders%20criticised%20the%20local%20administration%20and%20Indian%20Railways%2C%20citing%20inadequate%20festive%20season%20planning%20that%20led%20to%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20stampede%20at%20Bandra%20Terminus%20is%20very%20disturbing...%20This%20highlights%20the%20failure%20of%20Railways%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw.%20Insufficient%20trains%20during%20the%20festive%20season%20and%20local%20administrative%20shortcomings%20contributed%20to%20this%20mishap%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20NCP-SCP%20leader%20Clyde%20Crasto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730034780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2