quot%3BThere%20Was%20No%20Response%20To%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20Terror%20Attack%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20on%20Sunday%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20response%20from%20the%20Indian%20side%20after%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%2C%20and%20asserted%20that%20it%20won't%20be%20the%20case%20if%20such%20an%20incident%20were%20to%20recur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20should%20not%20have%20a%20repeat%20of%20what%20happened%20in%20Mumbai.%20That%20there%20was%20a%20terror%20attack%20and%20there%20was%20no%20response%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20told%20reporters%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMumbai%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20counter-terrorism%20for%20India%20and%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20India%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%2C%20it%20was%20chairing%20the%20counter-terrorism%20committee%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20held%20the%20counter-terrorism%20panel%20meeting%20in%20the%20same%20hotel%20that%20was%20hit%20by%20the%20terror%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20know%20that%20India%20is%20standing%20strong%20against%20terrorism.%20We%20are%20today%20leaders%20in%20fighting%20terrorism%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20talk%20of%20zero%20tolerance%20against%20terror%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20when%20somebody%20does%20something%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20response%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20have%20to%20expose.%20It%20is%20not%20acceptable%20that%20you%20are%20doing%20business%20during%20daytime%20and%20indulging%20in%20terror%20during%20the%20night%20and%20I%20have%20to%20pretend%20that%20everything%20is%20okay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20India%20will%20not%20accept%20it.%20This%20is%20what%20has%20changed%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20expose%20terrorism%20and%20we%20will%20act%20where%20we%20have%20to%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20also%20said%20India%20and%20China%20would%20soon%20resume%20patrolling%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20restoring%20the%20arrangement%20as%20it%20was%20in%20April%202020%2C%20before%20the%20border%20standoff%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20expect%20to%20return%20to%20pre-October%2031%2C%202020%2C%20patrolling%20arrangements%20in%20areas%20like%20Demchok%20and%20Depsang.%20This%20will%20take%20some%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730032620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fhraj6kb_jaishankar_625x300_26_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthere-was-no-response-to-26-11-mumbai-terror-attack-jaishankar-6884945%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20on%20Sunday%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20response%20from%20the%20Indian%20side%20after%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%2C%20and%20asserted%20that%20it%20won't%20be%20the%20case%20if%20such%20an%20incident%20were%20to%20recur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthere-was-no-response-to-26-11-mumbai-terror-attack-jaishankar-6884945%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20To%20Face%20Major%20'Bowling'%20Crisis%20In%20Near%20Future%3F%20Report%20Makes%20Grim%20Claim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20qualification%20for%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20in%20June%20next%20year%20is%20hanging%20in%20balance%20and%20even%20if%20they%20make%20the%20grade%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20time%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20massive%20surprise%20if%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20stays%20available%20for%20the%20next%20two-year%20WTC%20cycle.%20Ditto%20for%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%2C%20who%20will%20be%2041%20by%20then.%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20the%20two%20supremely%20fit%20men%2C%20will%20be%2039.%20The%20embarrassing%20Test%20series%20defeat%20at%20home%20against%20New%20Zealand%20has%20already%20triggered%20a%20debate%20around%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20a%20few%20seniors.%20Ravi%20Shastri%20could%20only%20empathize%20with%20Gambhir.%20%26quot%3BNew%20Zealand%20have%20beaten%20them%20(India)%20handsomely%20in%20both%20the%20Test%20matches.%20It's%20food%20for%20thought%20(on%20series%20loss).%20He%20(Gambhir)%20has%20just%20taken%20over%20the%20job.%20It's%20never%20easy%20being%20coach%20of%20a%20team%20that%20has%20such%20a%20big%20following%2C%26quot%3B%20Shastri%20said%20while%20commentating%20during%20the%20second%20Test%20in%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20still%20early%20days%20in%20his%20career%20as%20a%20coach.%20But%20he'll%20soon%20learn.%26quot%3B%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20India%20are%20looking%20at%20a%20tough%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%20four%20world-class%20match-winners%20are%20expected%20to%20bid%20adieu%20to%20the%20game%20one%20by%20one%20in%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years%20and%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20is%20in%20an%20unenviable%20position%20as%20head%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20multiple%20options%20available%20in%20batting%20but%20India%20may%20struggle%20to%20find%20good%20bowlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Shami%2C%20even%20if%20he%20comes%20back%2C%20is%20at%20the%20end%20of%20his%20glorious%2010-year-run%20for%20India%20and%20both%20Akash%20Deep%20and%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20are%20more%20than%20decent%20bowlers%20even%20as%20they%20do%20not%20have%20the%20menacing%20effect%20of%20Shami%20when%20Bumrah%20is%20operating%20from%20other%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20problem%20is%20the%20next-in-line%20bowlers.%20There's%20Avesh%20Khan%20and%20Khaleel%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20are%20quick%20bowlers%20but%20consistency%20and%20fitness%20has%20been%20their%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavdeep%20Saini's%20pace%20has%20dropped%20and%20his%20best%20years%20are%20behind%20him.%20Umran%20Malik%20has%20already%20lost%20his%20way%20and%20Mukesh%20Kumar%2C%20Vyshak%20Vijaykumar%2C%20Vidwath%20Kaverappa%20don't%20have%20that%20kind%20of%20pace%20that%20can%20put%20doubts%20in%20batters'%20minds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20is%20a%20gift%20of%20God%20and%20Shami%20a%20freak%20talent%20and%20unless%20someone%20like%20Mayank%20Yadav%20becomes%20fit%20and%20consistently%20available%20for%20longer%20version%2C%20the%20cupboard%20is%20actually%20bare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20area%20that%20could%20be%20a%20big%20concern%20is%20seam%20bowling%20all-rounder%20unless%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20who%20is%2030%20now%2C%20has%20an%20apparent%20change%20of%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Reddy%20is%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%20People%20in%20the%20know%20of%20things%20admitted%20that%20he%20is%20in%20the%20team%20because%20of%20'TINA'%20factor%20(There%20Is%20No%20Alternative)%20in%20this%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20willow%20wielders%20are%20in%20a%20better%20place%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20making%20one%20of%20the%20opener's%20slot%20his%20own%2C%20once%20Rohit%20is%20out%20of%20the%20Test%20scene%2C%20there%20are%20three%20candidates%20--%20two%20right%20handers%20Abhimanyu%20Easwaran%2C%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20--%20and%20southpaw%20B%20Sai%20Sudharsan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEaswaran%20has%20the%20most%20prolific%20record%20with%2027%20first-class%20hundreds%2C%20an%20average%20of%20nearly%2050%20in%2099%20red-ball%20games%20with%20four%20centuries%20in%20the%20last%20four%20games%20which%20prompted%20his%20selection%20as%20reserve%20opener%20for%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEaswaran%20is%20more%20of%20a%20grafter%20in%20the%20Cheteshwar%20Pujara%20mould%20but%20he%20has%20been%20in%20the%20Indian%20team's%20periphery%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20perception%20about%20Easwaran%20that%20he%20never%20scores%20in%20big%20games%20and%20pressure%20situations.%20Two%20Ranji%20trophy%20finals%2C%20three%20semi-finals%20and%20three%20quarter-finals%20without%20a%20half-century%20doesn't%20speak%20highly%20about%20his%20temperament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20in%20point%20is%20the%20only%20game%20that%20he%20failed%20in%20five%20domestic%20red%20ball%20matches%20this%20season%20was%20the%20Duleep%20Trophy%20opener%20where%20the%20opposition%20bowling%20attack%20had%20Avesh%20Khan%2C%20Akash%20Deep%20and%20Khaleel%20Ahmed%2C%20easily%20the%20best%20combination%20in%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaikwad%20is%20a%20terrific%20white-ball%20cricketer%20but%20only%20seven%20first-class%20hundreds%20in%2035%20games%20isn't%20what%20Test%20team%20would%20be%20looking%20at%20although%20his%20aggressive%20game%20might%20at%20times%20work%20in%20specific%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20brings%20us%20to%20B%20Sai%20Sudharsan%2C%20the%20left-hander%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20who%20has%20a%20good%20technique%2C%20sound%20temperament%20and%20an%20appetite%20for%20big%20runs.%20He%20recently%20played%20for%20the%20County%20team%20Surrey.%20He%20can%20bat%20as%20an%20opener%20and%20also%20at%20number%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20slot%20is%20the%20most%20envious%20one%20--%20Virat%20Kohli's.%20Devdutt%20Padikkal%2C%20who%20scored%20a%20fine%20half-century%20on%20Test%20debut%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20stylish%20batters%20going%20around%2C%20is%20an%20exciting%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20Pant%20is%20like%20MS%20Dhoni%2C%20there%20is%20very%20little%20chance%20any%20keeper-batter%20can%20come%20near%20him%20in%20next%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarfaraz%20Khan%20has%20started%20brilliantly%20in%20the%20five%20Tests%20so%20far%20but%20whether%20he%20is%20that%20ideal%20all-conditions%20No.%206%20in%20the%20line-up%20will%20be%20known%20in%20Australia.%20Axar%20Patel%20is%20a%20terrific%20bowler%20for%20under-prepared%20surfaces%20and%20can%20also%20be%20a%20handy%20batter%20like%20Jadeja%20but%20his%20bowling%20could%20be%20exposed%20on%20surfaces%20that%20do%20not%20offer%20help.%20Jadeja%20could%20play%20as%20a%20pure%20batter%20in%20SENA%20countries%20but%20one%20can't%20be%20so%20sure%20about%20Axar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20Sundar%20overshadowed%20someone%20like%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20in%20Pune%20with%2011%20wickets%20and%20is%20a%20very%20handy%20batter%20as%202021%20Brisbane%20showed.%20Going%20forward%20in%20the%20post%20Ashwin-Jadeja%20era%2C%20Washington%20could%20be%20the%20single%20spin-all-rounder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730031960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fqd0885fg_cas_625x300_27_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-to-face-major-bowling-crisis-in-near-future-report-makes-grim-claim-6885720%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20qualification%20for%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20in%20June%20next%20year%20is%20hanging%20in%20balance%20and%20even%20if%20they%20make%20the%20grade%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20time%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20massive%20surprise%20if%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20stays%20available%20for%20the%20next%20two-year%20WTC%20cycle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mahindra%20Lifespace%20Q2%20resul