%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsunny-deols-latest-post-saying-miss-you-papa-to-dharmendra-leaves-fans-worried-esha-deol-bobby-deol-react-pics-inside%2Farticleshow%2F114655598.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Urban%20Vault%20takes%20on%20lease%20120%2C000%20sq%20ft%20office%20space%20in%20Bengaluru's%20CBD%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730029377000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Furban-vault-takes-on-lease-120-000-sq-ft-office-space-in-bengaluru-s-cbd-124102700332_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Established%20in%202018%2C%20Urban%20Vault%20has%20more%20than%2020%20lakh%20square%20feet%20of%20office%20space%20in%20its%20portfolio%2C%20comprising%20more%20than%2030%2C000%20desks%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGambhir%20Will%20Soon%20Learn...%26quot%3B%3A%20Shastri's%20Honest%20Verdict%20On%20India%20Coach%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20head%20coach%20Ravi%20Shastri%20came%20out%20in%20support%20of%20the%20current%20Indian%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20after%20the%20side%20conceded%20the%20ongoing%20Test%20series%20to%20New%20Zealand.%20India%2C%20captained%20by%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20marking%20their%20first%20Test%20series%20loss%20at%20home%20in%2012%20years.%20Shastri%20explained%20that%20since%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20is%20in%20the%20early%20phase%20of%20his%20coaching%20stint%20with%20the%20national%20team%2C%20there%20is%20still%20enough%20time%20on%20hand.%20Indian%20batters%20got%20the%20taste%20of%20their%20own%20medicine%20as%20the%20Kiwi%20spin%20attack%20led%20by%20Mitchell%20Santner%2C%20who%20took%2013%20wickets%20in%20the%20match%2C%20trapped%20the%20hosts%20in%20their%20own%20spin%20trap%20and%20defeated%20India%20by%20113%20runs%20to%20secure%20the%20series%202-0%20with%20a%20game%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNew%20Zealand%20have%20beaten%20them%20(India)%20handsomely%20in%20both%20the%20Test%20matches.%20It's%20food%20for%20thought%20(on%20series%20loss).%20He%20(Gambhir)%20has%20just%20taken%20over%20the%20job.%20It%20is%20never%20easy%20being%20coach%20of%20a%20team%20that%20has%20such%20a%20big%20following.%20It%20is%20still%20early%20days%20in%20his%20career%20as%20a%20coach.%20But%20he'll%20soon%20learn%2C%26quot%3B%20Shastri%20said%2C%20while%20on%20commentary%20during%20the%20second%20Test%20in%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20New%20Zealand%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20elected%20to%20bat%20first.%20Half-centuries%20from%20Devon%20Conway%20(76%20in%20141%20balls%2C%20with%2011%20fours)%20and%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20(65%20in%20105%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20placed%20Kiwis%20in%20a%20strong%20position%20at%20197%2F3%2C%20with%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20(3%2F41)%20being%20the%20only%20one%20to%20have%20made%20some%20dents%20into%20the%20batting.%20Floodgates%20opened%20for%20wickets%20after%20Conway's%20dismissal%2C%20with%20comeback%20man%20Washington%20Sundar%20(7%2F59)%20getting%20the%20remaining%20wickets%20to%20get%20NZ%20to%20259%20all%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20was%20tasked%20to%20overcome%20this%20rather%20modest%20total%20and%20gain%20a%20sizeable%20lead.%20After%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20dismissal%20for%20a%20duck%2C%20youngsters%20Shubman%20Gill%20(30%20in%2072%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20and%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20(30%20in%2060%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries)%20tried%20forming%20a%20partnership.%20However%2C%20their%20effort%20was%20cut%20short%20at%2049%20runs.%20Just%20like%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20dismissal%20of%20a%20set%20Gill%20paved%20way%20for%20Mitchell%20Santner%20to%20run%20through%20the%20Indian%20line%20up.%20Santner%20(7%2F53)%20and%20Glenn%20Phillips%20(2%2F26)%20made%20Indian%20batters%20dance%20to%20their%20tunes%20on%20their%20own%20pitches%2C%20skittling%20them%20out%20for%20just%20156%20runs.%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20top-scored%20with%2038%20in%2046%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKiwis%20got%20themselves%20in%20a%20commanding%20position%20in%20their%20second%20innings.%20Led%20by%20skipper%20Tom%20Latham's%2086%20in%20133%20balls%2C%20with%2010%20fours%20and%20some%20important%20contributions%20from%20Phillips%20(48%20in%2082%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20two%20sixes)%20and%20Tom%20Blundell%20(41%20in%2083%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours)%2C%20Kiwis%20increased%20their%20103-run%20first%20inning%20lead%20to%20a%20lead%20of%20358%20runs%2C%20being%20skittled%20out%20for%20255%20after%20some%20fine%20bowling%20on%20first%20session%20of%20day%20three%20by%20spinners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESundar%20(4%2F56)%20once%20again%20lead%20the%20bowling%20from%20the%20front%2C%20with%20Jadeja%20(3%2F72)%20and%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20(2%2F97)%20wiping%20the%20lower-middle%20order%20and%20tail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20chase%20of%20359%2C%20India%20got%20a%20fine%20start%20from%20opener%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20who%20stitched%20a%20valuable%2062-run%20stand%20with%20Shubman%20Gill%20(23%20in%2031%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries).%20However%2C%20after%20Jaiswal's%20dismissal%20for%2077%20in%2065%20balls%2C%20with%20nine%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes%2C%20India%20never%20recovered%2C%20falling%20a%20prey%20to%20Kiwi%20spinners%20and%20bundled%20out%20for%20245%2C%20losing%20the%20test%20by%20113%20runs.%20With%20this%20India%20also%20registered%20its%20first%20home%20series%20loss%20in%2012%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESantner%20(6%2F104)%20was%20once%20again%20the%20star%2C%20taking%2013%20wickets%20in%20the%20match%2C%20with%20Phillips%20(two%20wickets)%20and%20Ajaz%20(one%20wicket)%20also%20offering%2