icalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F372310%2Fcyclone-dana-impact-areas-trains-and-flights-affected-schools-cancelled-safety-measures-for-odisha-and-west-bengal%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Pav%20Bhaji%20at%2012%20Was%20My%20First%20Dish%E2%80%99%3A%20Your%20Food%20Lab%E2%80%99s%20Sanjyot%20Keer%20on%20Popularising%20Bite-Sized%20Recipes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20quick%20scroll%20through%20Chef%20Sanjyot%20Keer%E2%80%99s%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20%E2%80%98Your%20Food%20Lab%2C%E2%80%99%20reveals%20his%20fascination%20for%20letting%20indigenous%20ingredients%20shine.%20Launched%20in%202016%20to%20showcase%20detailed%20yet%20simple%20food%20videos%2C%20Keer%20is%20known%20for%20coaxing%20flavours%20out%20of%20the%20most%20unassuming%20staples%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20His%20videos%20chronicle%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20culinary%20glory%2C%20from%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%3Cem%3E%20tikki%20chole%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20dish%20that%20combines%20potato%20patties%20with%20chickpea%20curry)%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F261268%2Fbiryani-map-of-india-taste-the-history-find-your-favourite-among-28-versions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echicken%20%3Cem%3Edum%20biryani%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E(meat%20marinated%20with%20short-grained%20rice)%2C%20fusion%20%3Cem%3Epaneer%20%3C%2Fem%3E(cottage%20cheese)%20burritos%2C%20and%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20classic%20%3Cem%3Ebhel%20puri%3C%2Fem%3E%20(street%20food%20snack).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterspersed%20amongst%20these%20short-form%20bites%20of%20deliciousness%20are%20clips%20of%20sit-downs%20of%20Chef%20Keer%20with%20industry%20luminaries.%20One%20particular%20clip%20that%20caught%20my%20eye%20featured%20British%20pop-star%20Ed%20Sheeran%20receiving%20a%20masterclass%20in%20making%20Maharashtrian%20%3Cem%3Emisal%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sprouts%20curry)%2C%20c