with%20the%20law%20(CCLs).%20We%E2%80%99ve%20had%20some%20initial%20engagements%2C%20but%20we%20recognise%20the%20unique%20challenges%20involved.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20vast%20area%2C%20and%20while%20we%E2%80%99re%20not%20quite%20there%20yet%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20develop%20a%20programme%20that%20supports%20CCLs%20in%20securing%20employment%20and%20managing%20their%20lives%20independently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20what%20message%20she%20would%20give%20to%20youth%20considering%20the%20programme%2C%20Ramya%20shares%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20programme%20is%20a%20bridge%20to%20independent%20living%20%E2%80%94%20it%20will%20empower%20you%20with%20the%20skills%20and%20confidence%20to%20stand%20on%20your%20own.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20an%20easy%20bridge%20to%20cross.%20The%20journey%20is%20filled%20with%20challenges%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20be%20there%20beside%20you%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way.%20By%20the%20time%20you%20transition%20out%2C%20our%20hope%20is%20that%20you%E2%80%99ll%20have%20the%20means%20to%20earn%20a%20livelihood%2C%20practical%20experience%2C%20enhanced%20skills%2C%20and%20some%20savings.%20More%20importantly%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20have%20a%20network%20of%20people%20to%20rely%20on%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20be%20part%20of%20that%20network.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20WeLive%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729774320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_040_11zon-1729768067.jpg%3Fw%3D1233%26ssl%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D372170%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20no%20safety%20nets%2C%20thousands%20of%20youth%20age%20out%20of%20childcare%20institutions%20at%2018.%20WeLive%20Foundation%20offers%20them%20more%20than%20just%20survival%20%E2%80%94%20it%20gives%20them%20the%20tools%20to%20thrive.%22%2C%22aut