%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C628%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jitender%20and%20Sarla%20have%20developed%20a%20profitable%20venture%20by%20selling%20moringa%20powder.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C402%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20data-recalc-dims%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371317%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJitender%20and%20Sarla%20have%20developed%20a%20profitable%20venture%20by%20selling%20moringa%20powder.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20an%20ICMR%20(Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research)%20report%20had%20revealed%20that%20an%20estimated%2056.4%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20disease%20burden%20was%20linked%20to%20unhealthy%20diets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJitender%E2%80%99s%20realisation%20fueled%20his%20determination%20to%20move%20back%20to%20his%20ancestral%20home%20in%20Mehmudpur%20village%20in%20Sonipat%20district%20of%20Haryana%2C%20alongside%20his%20wife%2C%20Sarla.