1200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C402%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20data-recalc-dims%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371318%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20ensures%20that%20the%20nutritional%20content%20of%20the%20leaves%20remains%20in%20the%20final%20product%20for%20distribution.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20importance%20of%20preserving%20the%20nutritional%20value%20of%20moringa%20leaves%2C%20Jitender%20and%20Sarla%20invested%20in%20a%20state-of-the-art%20drying%20setup%20that%20ensures%20optimal%20drying%20conditions%20while%20retaining%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20beneficial%20properties.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20plucking%20stems%20with%20leaves%2C%20we%20wash%20them%20twice%20and%20bundle%20seven%20to%20nine%20stems%20together%20so%20that%20each%20leaf%20is%20separated%20for%20easier%20drying%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarla%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20dry%20the%20leaves%20under%20large%20fans%20and%20also%20in%20a%20controlled%20greenhouse%20setup%2C%20where%20energy%20gets%20trapped%20and%20the%20temperature%20is%208-10%20degrees%20hotter%20than%20outside.%20After%2012%20hours%2C%20the%20leaves%20become%20crunchy%20and%20we%20separate%20them%20from%20the%20stems.%20We%20then%20make%20a%20coarse%20powder%20in%20a%20pulveriser%20and%20remove%20stalks%20before%20packaging%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20meticulous%20process%2C%20Jitender%20says%2C%20ensures%20that%20the%20nutritional%20content%20of%20the%20leaves%20remains%20in%20the%20final%20product%20for%20distribution.%20%E2%80%9CMoringa%20is%20a%20summer-loving%20plant%20in%20North%20India.%20We%20harvest%20leaves%20for%20about%20seven%20months%20between%20April%20and%20October%2C%20with%20the%20plant%20remaining%20dormant%20for%20the%20remaining%20five%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jitender%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarla%20points%20out%20that%20to%20ensure%20high-quality%20crop%20production%2C%20they%20adopted%20a%20jungle%20farming%20method.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20method%2C%20we%20do%20not%20till%20the%20soil%20and%20use%20weeds%20and%20other%20leaves%20as%20mulch.%20We%20also%20avoid%20harmful%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%20pesticides%2C%20and%20weedicides.%20This%20ensures%20that%20our%20soil%20has%20good%20aeration%20and%20high%20carbon%20content.%20You%20can%20only%20produce%20good-quality%20moringa%20leaves%20if%20your%20soil%20is%20fertile%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20to%20becoming%20a%20profitable%20venture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarla%20informs%20that%20about%201%2C000%20kg%20of%20dry%20powder%20can%20be%20produced%20from%20one%20acre%20of%20land.%20By%20selling%20a%20200-gram%20packet%20of%20moringa%20powder%2C%20the%20couple%20earns%20Rs%20650.%20On%20average%2C%20they%20make%20sales%20of%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20per%20month%20and%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20per%20acre%20every%20season.%20They%20established%20a%20customer%20base%20in%20metro%20cities%20like%20Delhi%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Gurugram%20primarily%20through%20word%20of%20mouth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20with%20two%20acres%20for%20cultivating%20moringa%20powder%2C%20but%20our%20demand%20is%20growing%20at%20twice%20the%20rate%20of%20our%20production.%20Next%20year%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20expand%20our%20moringa%20fields%20from%20four%20to%20eight%20acres%20and%20explore%20international%20markets%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jitender%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C628%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20employs%20many%20rural%20women%20to%20pluck%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20package%20moringa%20leaves%20powder.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C402%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%2